<p><a name="Talmudic_layout" id="Talmudic_layout"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Talmud&amp;action=edit&amp;section=45" title="Edit section: Talmudic layout">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Talmudic layout</span></h3>
<ul>
